# Privacy Statement

This privacy statement applies to the JakubTech Project demo tenant.

## Data Controller
JakubTech Project (Demo / Lab Environment)

## Purpose of Data Processing
This tenant is used for:
- Azure / Entra ID identity testing
- RBAC and PIM demonstrations
- Conditional Access and security policy labs
- Portfolio and learning projects

## Data Collected
- User names and email addresses
- Authentication and sign-in logs
- Device identifiers
- IP addresses
- Audit and activity logs

## Legal Basis
Processing is based on legitimate interest for technical testing and learning purposes.
All accounts are test or demo users.

## Data Retention
Logs and data are retained for a maximum of 90 days unless required longer for audit testing.

## Data Sharing
Data is not shared with third parties.
Microsoft acts as the data processor for cloud services.

## Security Measures
- Least privilege access
- Multi-Factor Authentication
- Conditional Access policies
- Activity logging and auditing

## Contact
For questions regarding this privacy statement, contact:

admin-ops@jakubtech.co.uk
